714
01:03:29,840 --> 01:03:31,760
[SPEAKER_01] Da, nevjerojatno.

715
01:03:31,760 --> 01:03:33,400
[SPEAKER_02] On je inače, znaš, Bog je takav,

716
01:03:33,400 --> 01:03:35,360
