717
01:03:35,360 --> 01:03:37,159
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ja nisam nikakvu krizu,

718
01:03:37,159 --> 01:03:38,159
[SPEAKER_01] ništa, ništa,

719
01:03:38,159 --> 01:03:40,539
[SPEAKER_01] nikad više u životu nisam zapavila cigaretu,

720
01:03:40,539 --> 01:03:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] ali nikakvu ni krizu.

721
01:03:42,039 --> 01:03:44,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se osjećao kao nepušač.

722
01:03:44,980 --> 01:03:48,519
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, ali ja sam rekla tada,

723
01:03:48,519 --> 01:03:51,699
