724
01:03:51,699 --> 01:03:53,400
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam vidjela kao,

725
01:03:53,400 --> 01:03:56,179
[SPEAKER_01] dragi Bog, mi pokazuje da prestanem

726
01:03:56,179 --> 01:03:58,320
[SPEAKER_01] puši prekrižene cigarete i to i dalje,

727
01:03:58,320 --> 01:03:59,659
[SPEAKER_01] jer me je počeo srce lupati

728
01:03:59,659 --> 01:04:00,940
[SPEAKER_01] i misla sam da ću umrijeti.

729
01:04:00,940 --> 01:04:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se rekao, dobro, Bože,

730
01:04:02,000 --> 01:04:05,159
[SPEAKER_01] opraštam, može, opraštam.

731
01:04:08,039 --> 01:04:09,800
[SPEAKER_01] Samo da ovdje sad, ja umiru,

732
01:04:09,800 --> 01:04:11,360
[SPEAKER_01] njutko ne vidi da ja umirem.

733
01:04:11,360 --> 01:04:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] I onda sve se smiri,

734
01:04:13,800 --> 01:04:14,320
[SPEAKER_01] i onda ja mislim,

735
01:04:14,320 --> 01:04:15,239
[SPEAKER_01] a to sam ja umisla,

736
01:04:15,239 --> 01:04:16,440
[SPEAKER_01] halucinacija moja,

737
01:04:16,440 --> 01:04:18,840
[SPEAKER_01] ja uvijek ja volim tako zamišljati

738
01:04:18,840 --> 01:04:21,500
[SPEAKER_01] i ponovo u tom trenutku

739
01:04:21,500 --> 01:04:22,539
[SPEAKER_01] i onda to je,

740
01:04:22,539 --> 01:04:23,840
[SPEAKER_01] jer je to nije Bože čuda.

741
01:04:23,840 --> 01:04:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] Da, u istinu je.

742
01:04:24,960 --> 01:04:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] To je, evo, to je Bože.

743
01:04:26,800 --> 01:04:30,199
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, mi toliko imamo

744
01:04:30,199 --> 01:04:31,760
[SPEAKER_01] izravni Bože čuda

745
01:04:31,760 --> 01:04:34,500
[SPEAKER_01] u svom životu

746
01:04:34,500 --> 01:04:37,420
[SPEAKER_01] da, ja ne znam koliko bi trebalo

747
