757
01:04:55,760 --> 01:04:57,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ako pazite što Boga molite.

758
01:04:57,719 --> 01:04:58,980
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

759
01:04:58,980 --> 01:05:01,639
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, to je zapravo nevjerojatna priča,

