[SPEAKER_02] oprostim,

791
01:05:44,860 --> 01:05:45,780
[SPEAKER_02] ali opet isto ono,

792
01:05:45,780 --> 01:05:47,059
[SPEAKER_02] ja bi bušila gume i to.

793
01:05:48,519 --> 01:05:49,940
[SPEAKER_02] Kao to mi je skroz ok.

794
01:05:49,940 --> 01:05:51,900
[SPEAKER_02] I on kaže,

795
01:05:51,900 --> 01:05:53,579
[SPEAKER_02] ali zašto ti misliš

